{"tid":408404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心臟生係胸腔出面 俄妹:耶穌展示能力","createTime":"2017-09-21T07:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T01:06:43.000Z","uid":75969,"like":10,"dislike":146,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"282287ca367c15366969f487eaf5cf8f69555dc0","tid":408404,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170920/large/1505884613_64f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170920%2Flarge%2F1505884613_64f4.jpg&h=26351f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常人的心臟由肋骨保護，偏偏俄羅斯一位女童的心臟卻僅長於皮下，每次笑起來時心臟躍動清晰可見。<br />\n<br />\n片中女童相信是目前俄羅斯女童岡察洛娃（Virsaviya Borun-Goncharova），本報在兩年前也曾報道過她的情況。最近社交網站YouTube有題為「VirsaviyaWarrior」的新片段曝光，片中可見博倫的心臟僅由一層薄薄的皮膚包著，她笑時心臟凸出似個膨脹的汽球，並隨心跳收縮起伏。<br />\n<br />\n岡察洛娃患的是坎特雷爾五聯症（Pentalogy of Cantrell），此症又稱為胸腹症候群（Thoraco-Abdominal syndrome）。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雖然身有頑疾，但她仍然樂觀，在2015年接受訪問時曾這樣說：「我知道我的心臟長在外面，因為耶穌想展示他有能力製造像我這樣特別的事物。」<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n一家人當年由俄羅斯飛到美國波士頓求醫，但醫生警告她的高血壓令她無法接受手術，暫時未知情況有否改變。由於寒冷天氣會威脅到她的性命，故一家人後來搬到洛杉磯郊外荷李活，由於當地氣候較和暖，當她的心臟和暖時也較少不適。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170921/57232402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170921%2F57232402&d=MhMkvgyz0adl4zSqwv%2B4dV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=303cf6ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170921%2F57232402&h=8477e205\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170921/57232402</a><br />\n<br />\n片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbRedZsylL4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYbRedZsylL4&d=MhMkvgyz0adl4zSqwv%2B4dV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=942801e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbRedZsylL4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PSxJaC11HEQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPSxJaC11HEQ&d=MhMkvgyz0adl4zSqwv%2B4dV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b06a2b0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PSxJaC11HEQ</a><br />\n<br />\n好驚跳跳下會突然間爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26784f8e45f1f45ef524139e3be38ef002024fe7","tid":408404,"uid":240,"like":165,"dislike":25,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"陰公 個春袋生左係心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2072c76d6fb4e99ebc551c8c605e6e8c1701eecc","tid":408404,"uid":53121,"like":177,"dislike":7,"score":170,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"大個左比男朋友揸揸下波揸錯左就大獲"},{"pid":"e894fc3c213e4f367b7862e6b9678e87a4e7ae2e","tid":408404,"uid":19557,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"好危險姐"},{"pid":"a536b5bda808d7d079655317cd8be00f06eda7f3","tid":408404,"uid":11270,"like":50,"dislike":4,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/residentevil/images/c/c5/RE_Tyrant.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091109173807\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fresidentevil%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc5%2FRE_Tyrant.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20091109173807&h=5de1000c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58398a713e7f1a61ce6f9f861d6dfd2d58fa3815","tid":408404,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/residentevil/images/c/c5/RE_Tyrant.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091109173807\